{"tid":1467950,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[呢 場 運 動 已 經 玩 撚 完] 屌 柒 和 理 非 ， 屌 柒 勇 武 派","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:45:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T00:24:09.000Z","uid":114891,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"82a1f926818e3640c1c4f3020c026d53a5632d4b","tid":1467950,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:45:32.000Z","msg":"標題黨，屌完就麻煩認真做個賽後分析。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">[心理戰] 唔好再講和理非 唔好再講勇武<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427484</a></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n先唔好討論有無鬼先，發覺今日大家都好似<span style=\"color: red;\">二元分立</span>咁樣，點樣做到<span style=\"color: red;\">不分化不割蓆</span>呀，我地首先要做到既係<span style=\"color: red;\">和而不同</span>呀，呢個係我地同藍絲班撚樣既分別。<br />\n<br />\n1. 朝早有人講阻唔阻旅客登機講到就黎打交<br />\n今日既目的係<span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓機場</span>，現場有兩批人，一班話唔好搞旅客話會失民意，一班話去阻旅客登機，差少少開拖，要做到癱瘓機場，就算落唔落去攔班旅客，班旅客點都會好撚躁架喇，你試下你去旅行滯留機場出唔番去你躁唔躁，所以我地必須要記住目的唔係玩鳩班旅客，攔佢地係其中一個癱瘓機場既方法，當然呢個唔係最好既方法，但係又係唔係代表要直接話＂而家唔撚同意你地去攔喎，你地唔撚准去搞旅客＂呢？我唔係想兩邊各打五十大板然後收工，大家就係要brainstorm更多可行既方法，例如話係留番一條counter比人check in咁，機場一樣係會變到收皮架，使唔使同手足鬧交呢？<br />\n<br />\n2. 家庭觀眾既關心<br />\n我好明白唔少家庭觀眾未必可以到現場支持，所以會睇住直播提供意見，大家睇住直播見到圍住隻狗圍左幾個鐘個畫面對大眾印象好差，又或者見到形勢有危險希望手足要走唔好出事，呢D關注對落場既手足其實都<span style=\"color: red;\">非常重要</span>，因為你地手上有最多既資訊，現場手足都未必有咁多時間睇到突發消息，所以我唔會用冷氣軍師四隻字，不過希望大家講意見前先代入下落場手足既角色，佢地一打開部電話，見到大家鬧豬隊友，見到大家鬧場運動玩撚完，你覺得佢地會點諗先，細力屌係可以，不過屌完真係比番D正面D既message同埋執行到既方案，鼓勵番落場手足，<span style=\"color: red;\">不分化不割蓆</span>。<br />\n<br />\n3. 捉鬼之後既處理<br />\n之前鳩up講過要錫春袋呀之類，估唔到落到場又真係捉到鬼，大家第一次捉到鬼都好熱血，群情洶湧真係準備好錫春袋，我好明白大家經過之前幾星期見到落單狗同埋黑社會，已經有共識唔反對私了，不過要留意番呢度係機場，好撚多記者，好撚多鏡頭，好撚多未black bloc既手足，比記者影到，藍媒好黃媒好佢點都要播出街，個觀感一定唔會好，最最最撚重要係<span style=\"color: red;\">出師無名</span>，所以並唔係一個錫春袋既好地方，見到出面有巴打出左個post話要set軍規我好認同，以武制暴應該無人會反對，手足做野最緊要出師有名，學班狗成日講要適當武力，咪除鳩佢褲囉。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">FYI<br />\n經過今晚之後 覺唔覺前線手足要set返一堆軍規？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1465135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1465135</a></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n結論：<br />\n和而不同，屌人可以，字眼好少少，唔撚好講豬隊友三隻字，屌完比番幾個有建設性既suggestion，共識番個軍規，兄弟爬山，各自努力。<br />\n<br />\n最後：<br />\n是日MVP<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=513448716072445\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D513448716072445&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ijx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=00948820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=513448716072445</a><br />\n<br />\n有D論點唔知放邊度：<br />\n至於有D燥到仆街既滯留旅客，都見到有D英文好既手足去做文宣解釋香港發生緊咩事，撇除會打人既旅客必須ignore，唔好理佢地，唔好同佢地打，開明既旅客先係我地既宣傳對象。<br />\nLaser手足要練下對準少少，對狗好對CCTV好，小心誤中手足。"},{"pid":"55632857e54d5a11975b7515d22891f50dec1b59","tid":1467950,"uid":229840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化，不割席！<br />\n核彈都唔割！！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"8bdb485436230571e0e1ff2c7c1a211644baa993","tid":1467950,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"819cd4c8eaf09a2a60b8518cb10e1846245d34a4","tid":1467950,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"caeb06b1e487b293145231942a9ae09cc73f7993","tid":1467950,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:59.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"381f250816d8c54158748e3e5cd247504eabd210","tid":1467950,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:48:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8f0ea88eedb93e7822af5eb03ff0f11a12bc78c7","tid":1467950,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:48:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cc9b40a37f9898820fa509cfcd343782ea62ba16","tid":1467950,"uid":33498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:48:55.000Z","msg":"冇和理非 冇勇武派<br />\n只有做緊唔同野既手足"},{"pid":"4d1f32768f6ef61b07940f42f12529daa77b2e95","tid":1467950,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:49:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"66afe03f3d68113ff5cdcf695ca3bbf9f68f06b8","tid":1467950,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:49:36.000Z","msg":"光復香港之前不如先光復連登<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc75f27f0b4504cb83b1965fef30334ae281c914","tid":1467950,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:49:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"002c387a3d17961798a6f5cc99536a6205eb904d","tid":1467950,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:49:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c881bb91abec9a45936910285d7450eba81d9c72","tid":1467950,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:50:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1eff760a0919421c804b1102e4ef9a0296fc6e98","tid":1467950,"uid":52609,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:50:18.000Z","msg":"記住所有手足共識：<br />\n1. 不傷害記者，不阻礙記者工作<br />\n2. 不傷害急救人員，不阻礙急救人員工作<br />\n3. 不任意攻擊一般平民及其財產<br />\n4. 不使用酷刑<br />\n<br />\n如果有人太激動破壞共識，拉開佢一邊先<br />\n死都唔聽，有機會係狗扮示威者帶風向<br />\n獨立思考，唔好中伏<br />\n<br />\n捉鬼正確方法 (PR最好睇)<br />\n1. 詢問<br />\n2. 控制，防止逃跑<br />\n3. 搵記者，由記者盤問（811記者問黑警扮示威者咁樣）<br />\n5. 睇證件、影相<br />\n6. 散水，不包圍<br />\n<br />\n721 805 811"},{"pid":"db78ce8723548603881bddeeb9fbdc7dbc710cf5","tid":1467950,"uid":181350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:50:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"72f9ce4cdfebc79787e936a6f78aedb36c101dc6","tid":1467950,"uid":3055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:08.000Z","msg":"睇下一直企係我地呢邊既記者點講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467858\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467858</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/DotDotNews/videos/2301192406624132/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDotDotNews%2Fvideos%2F2301192406624132%2F&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ijx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=d85f5ebe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/DotDotNews/videos/2301192406624132/</a><br />\n唔好先入為主覺得紅媒抹黑我地，受訪記者係外藉香港人，一直企係示威者呢邊，亦都係撐天琦。被爆眼女手足單野佢都有出片做證。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RichScotford5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRichScotford5%2F&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ijx9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=6cc0d2cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RichScotford5/</a>"},{"pid":"1c6c5cc5b07315fe78444cd7f894a65fb9554f88","tid":1467950,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6347e35abf53bf1b44bd6f9619b744b6a1dcf9db","tid":1467950,"uid":249741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:52:05.000Z","msg":"革命信條<br />\n1. 不能傷害無辜<br />\n2. 隱藏自己身份的同時，謹記這場革命的初衷<br />\n3. 永遠不會背叛、離棄同伴<br />\n<br />\n參考自 刺客信條 中的3條戒條<br />\n原文:<br />\n1. Stay your blade from the flesh of an innocent<br />\n2. Hide in plain sight<br />\n3. Never compromise the Brotherhood<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n&ldquo;萬事皆虛，萬事皆允。(Nothing is true,everything is permitted.)&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n大家推比前線手足睇"},{"pid":"bd37efe1ab5ed8cb5dd5baaa688e07a93a3a4df2","tid":1467950,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:52:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8d280b57a879ab0d5a0e7a30da808689f0c4527a","tid":1467950,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:53:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fa4b8ad2e2257e73cd351f39958a18a516500717","tid":1467950,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:53:05.000Z","msg":"唔玩cancel 玩<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">delay</span></span></strong>!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464220</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你地老母 你地有無搭過飛機架？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464168</a><br />\n<br />\n機場現時既建議方法，希望多人睇到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464007</a><br />\n<br />\n8.13機場策略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463429</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：機場人流<br />\n<br />\n[和你飛] 外國人旅遊，中國人滯留<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463771</a><br />\n<br />\n離境大堂被阻外國人：應該控制，而唔係阻止登記<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463192</a>"},{"pid":"0765d3e516c781ae77fa021b822c9653753f7092","tid":1467950,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:54:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"21ac72b7cd7c6446921309ac98685f793be7ed40","tid":1467950,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:55:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4548bd54e2c8b1bf6d382c58984fc967a81be9d9","tid":1467950,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1d2287b183c3db2151ee7cc79472d12c2009d6bc","tid":1467950,"uid":114891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:00:57.000Z","msg":"push"}]}